query:
SELECT brand, COUNT(*) as count 
FROM watches 
WHERE brand IN ('Audemars Piguet', 'Patek Philippe', 'Rolex', 'Vacheron Constantin', 
                'A. Lange & Söhne', 'Jaeger-LeCoultre', 'IWC', 'Omega', 'Cartier')
GROUP BY brand
ORDER BY count DESC
